# 9) API calls with Axios 
    1. Get Started With Axios
    2. Make API Calls
    3. Component LifeCycle
    4. Creating Services

    INSTALLATION

    (Install Axios)
    sudo npm install -g json-server
    npm install axios

    run the following command to create a sepret server for API
    json-server --watch (file like)db.json

    most commonly used client API library
    AXIOS
    a) GET, POST, PUT AND DELETE request
    b) Add authentication to each request
    c) Set timeout if request take too long
    d) Configure Default for every request
    e) intercept requests to create middleware
    f) Handle errors and cancel requests properly
    g) properly serialize and deserializ requesta and responses

    axios request example
    
    axios.get('www.example.com')
    .then(response => {
        console.log(response.data)
    })
    .catch(error => {
         console.log(error)
    })


udpate all packages command
npm outdate
npm update @vue/cli-plugin-label
npm update (all plugin)

